(define/contract (count num1 num2 min_sum max_sum)
  (-> string? string? exact-integer? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  
  (define MOD 1000000007)
  
  (define (digit-sum n)
    (if (= n 0) 0 (+ (modulo n 10) (digit-sum (quotient n 10)))))

  (define (find-good-integers low high)
    (if (> low high)
        0
        (let* ((ds (digit-sum low))
               (next (+ low 1)))
          (if (and (>= ds min_sum) (<= ds max_sum))
              (modulo (+ 1 (find-good-integers next high)) MOD)
              (find-good-integers next high)))))
  
  (define (fast-count start end)
    (let loop ((i start) (count 0))
      (if (> i end) count
          (let ((sum (digit-sum i)))
            (if (and (>= sum min_sum) (<= sum max_sum))
                (loop (+ i 1) (modulo (+ count 1) MOD))
                (loop (+ i 1) count))))))

  (fast-count (string->number num1) (string->number num2)))
